HR 286 Original 2026 Regular Session Owen
Requests Louisiana Economic Development to conduct a study on the feasibility of
establishing a Louisiana Rural Community Energy and Education Investment Program,
comprised of tax incentives and public-private partnerships to finance renewable energy,
energy efficiency, and workforce infrastructure improvements in rural communities.
Requests a written report of its findings no later than Feb. 1, 2027.
